m" href="/articles/dzhon-gill-spravochnik/"> <span class="gb-series-mark gb-series-mark--label toc-item__num">Справ.</span> <div class="toc-item__info"> <b>Справочник по Гиллу</b> <small>8 мин</small> </div> <div class="toc-item__chevron"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"></path></svg></div> </a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="toc-overlay" id="partTocOverlay"> <div class="toc-sheet" role="dialog" aria-label="Введение · Исторический контекст"> <div class="toc-sheet__handle"></div> <div class="toc-sheet__head toc-sheet__head--grid"> <button class="back" id="backToSeries" aria-label="Назад к серии"> <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg> </button> <div class="toc-head-txt"> <div class="lab">Введение · Содержание</div> <h3>Исторический контекст</h3> </div> </div> <div class="toc-sheet__scroll-bar"><i style="--scroll-pct:0%"></i></div> <div class="toc-sheet__list" id="gbs2PartToc"> <div class="toc-part-item is-current"> <span aria-hidden="true" class="gb-roman gb-series-mark toc-part-item__num">I</span> <div class="toc-part-item__info"> <b>От пуритан к диссентерам</b> <small style="color:var(--gb-accent,#7a2e2e)">● Глава 1</small> </div> <div class="toc-part-item__progress"><i style="width:0%"></i></div> </div><a class="toc-part-item" href="#sec-particular-vs-general"> <span aria-hidden="true" class="gb-roman gb-series-mark toc-part-item__num">II</span> <div class="toc-part-item__info"> <b>Партикулярные и генеральные</b> <small>Глава 2</small> </div> <div class="toc-part-item__progress"><i></i></div> </a><a class="toc-part-item" href="#sec-great-ejection"> <span aria-hidden="true" class="gb-roman gb-series-mark toc-part-item__num">III</span> <div class="toc-part-item__info"> <b>Тень 1662: Великое изгнание</b> <small>Глава 3</small> </div> <div class="toc-part-item__progress"><i></i></div> </a><a class="toc-part-item" href="#sec-clarendon"> <span aria-hidden="true" class="gb-roman gb-series-mark toc-part-item__num">IV</sp