y-rossii/cover-07-vsehib.svg" alt="" width="600" height="315" loading="lazy" decoding="async"></span><span><span class="gbs2-pn">7 · 26 мин</span><span class="gbs2-pt">1944: один союз</span><span class="gbs2-ps">ВСЕХиБ, Братский Вестник, ХВЕ и Прибалтика</span></span><span class="gbs2-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span></a><a class="gbs2-part" href="../iniciativnaya-gruppa/"><span class="gbs2-thumb"><img src="../../images/baptisty-rossii/cover-08-initiative.svg" alt="" width="600" height="315" loading="lazy" decoding="async"></span><span><span class="gbs2-pn">8 · 25 мин</span><span class="gbs2-pt">Инициативная группа</span><span class="gbs2-ps">1960–1966: Положение, письмо, Оргкомитет и</span></span><span class="gbs2-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span></a><a class="gbs2-part" href="../podpolnaya-pechat/"><span class="gbs2-thumb"><img src="../../images/baptisty-rossii/cover-09-samizdat.svg" alt="" width="600" height="315" loading="lazy" decoding="async"></span><span><span class="gbs2-pn">9 · 23 мин</span><span class="gbs2-pt">Подпольная печать</span><span class="gbs2-ps">Вестник спасения, Вестник истины, Совет ро</span></span><span class="gbs2-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span></a><a class="gbs2-part" href="../spravochnik/"><span class="gbs2-thumb"><img src="../../images/baptisty-rossii/cover-10-reference.svg" alt="" width="600" height="315" loading="lazy" decoding="async"></span><span><span class="gbs2-pn">10 · 27 мин</span><span class="gbs2-pt">Справочник</span><span class="gbs2-ps">Люди, даты, документы, спорные факты и ист</span></span><span class="gbs2-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span></a></nav><section class="gbs2-current" aria-label="Текущая часть" style="--gbs2-cover:url(../../images/baptisty-rossii/cover-04-peterburg.svg)"><div class="gbs2-current-cover" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="gbs2-current-body"><div class="gbs2-current-label">Сейчас</div><div class="gbs2-current-title">Петербургское пробуждение: Редсток, Пашков и Проханов</div><div class="gbs2-